eses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"大量 'context canceled' 错误可能与请求处理超时或服务之间的通信问题有关。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"error\\\":\\\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该日志分析表明前端服务可能在处理请求时存在问题，需要进一步监视或审查请求的上下文处理逻辑以解决问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"context_canceled\",\n    \"transport_closing\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency increase observed in 'ProductCatalogService/GetProduct' (Frontend→ProductCatalog) with an increase from ~11ms to ~58 seconds during the anomaly.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg: 11480.30 µs | Anomaly avg: 58215771.56 µs | Occurrence: 26.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ListProducts API\",\n      \"reason\": \"Further delay in 'ProductCatalogService/ListProducts' between Frontend and ProductCatalog during anomaly, causing cascading slowness.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal avg: 1968.26 µs | Anomaly avg: 56452060.71 µs | Occurrence: 16.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Encountered frequent 'context canceled' and 'transport is closing' errors possibly due to delay in downstream services.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error: 13 (HTTP status code: 500) with ~146 occurrences.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
